ISLAMABAD, Apr 9 (APP): Federal Minister for Railways Khawaja Saad Rafique here on Sunday directed the relevant department of Pakistan Railways to pay the pensions and salaries of employees by April 18 for Eid-ul-Fitr celebrations.
In a statement issue here, the minister directed to further improve the ‘Iftar’ arrangements in Green Line Train which run between Islamabad to Karachi.
